      • presentSignUp

        public MoneytreeAuthOptions.Builder presentSignUp(boolean presentSignUp)
        Parameters:
        presentSignUp - You should set true if you want to show `SignUp` page when the SDK shows WebView to start authorization flow. Otherwise it will show the Login page.

      • authorizationHandler

        public MoneytreeAuthOptions.Builder authorizationHandler(Authorization.OnCompletionListener handler)
        Parameters:
        handler - A handler that runs when getting a token or gets errors. It works only in `PKCE` flow. The authorization token is passed to the Authorization.OnCompletionListener#onSuccess(String) if successful. Otherwise the error is passed to the Authorization.OnCompletionListener#onError(MoneytreeLinkException)

      • email

        public MoneytreeAuthOptions.Builder email(java.lang.String email)
        Parameters:
        email - An initial email address where it will show in the Signup/Login form. Default is null.

      • region

        Parameters:
        region - Region where a user belongs to.

      • codeGrantTypeOptions

        public MoneytreeAuthOptions.Builder codeGrantTypeOptions(MoneytreeAuthOptions.CodeGrantTypeOptions options)
        Parameters:
        options - A specific option set for `authorization flow for the grant code type`. Default is null but it requires in that auth flow.

      • forceLogout

        public MoneytreeAuthOptions.Builder forceLogout(boolean forceLogout)
